===========================================================
Dockerfile for a Ubuntu Python base image
===========================================================


DESCRIPTION:
============

Based on phusion/baseimage
    See https://registry.hub.docker.com/u/phusion/baseimage/


DOCKER IMAGE
============

sudo docker build -t scioncc/scion_python:1.0 .


USAGE
=====

sudo docker run --rm -it scioncc/scion_python:1.0 /bin/bash -l

